Boblight for Raspberry-PI 2.1, optimized.

This new version is also working with the new enigma2 version (0.8r6).
The old Raspberry-PI version was crashing with this new Enigma2 version.

- Added new lightpack support for firmware < 6.2 and > 6.3
- Some new features to make less CPU and more stable
- This version can also used on cygwin to use it on Windows
 
